// Introduction

1.3
Objectives

Our objective is to exploit graph database to find 
influential nodes in twitter social network based on particular domain.


1.4
Report Organisation
This report is organized as - 
Chapter 2 : It focuses on social network, its applications and gives detailed survey of approaches and techniques for
influentical analysis in social twitter network. It provides detail information of graph database,its importance in social network analysis. It
introduces Neo4j its importance and application. Chapter 3 : Describes our work
in the project and provides overview of the future plan.
